er einen und die angesichts des Fremden und Neuen verunsicherten Erklärungsversuche der anderen – all dies lässt sich dem heutigen Leser nur dann vermitteln, wenn man die Quellen, wie in diesem Band, in ihren geschichtlichen, kulturpolitischen und biographischen Kontexten erschließt.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 7aART / General.2bisacsh1 aAragon, Louis, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBazin, Germain, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCassou, Jean, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCollombat, Sophie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDegand, Léon, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDemarne, Pierre, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDescargues, Pierre, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDymschitz, Alexander, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aElgar, Frank, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEstienne, Charles, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFischer, Klaus Jürgen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGießler, Rupert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGindertael, Roger Van, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGoldschmidt, Werner, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrohmann, Will, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHaftmann, Werner, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHartung, Hans, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHausenstein, Wilhelm, econtributor.4ctb4https